The paper focuses on the forensic analysis of Android cloud-based apps, which involves examining the data stored on the device and in the cloud. This falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper discusses the analysis of user authentication credentials, which relates to cybersecurity (cs.CY) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper involves analyzing app databases, which falls under the category of databases (cs.DB).
